==Web UI and templates==

===How do I create a new HTML template for my Action?===

----

===How do I add a stylesheet to `<head/>`? ===

{{{
<@ecdb.include_css url="any/relative/or/absolute/url" />
}}}

This macro can appear anywhere in a template.

----

===How do I add a javascript to `<head/>`? ===

{{{
<@ecdb.include_js url="any/relative/or/absolute/url" />
}}}

This macro can appear anywhere in a template.

----

===How do I create those right-floated context boxes? ===

{{{
    <@ecdb.context_box title="Page Title"> 
        Your content here.
    </@>
}}}    
Additional args to the above macro:

    # id          - optional string - DOM id of the HTML div
    # title       - optional string - title text for this box
    # prepend     - optional boolean - if true, content is prepended instead of appended.

Context boxes can appear anywhere in the template.